To run the unit tests, use the following:

    phpunit --configuration phpunit.xml

You can also run tests for just the controllers:

    phpunit --configuration phpunit.xml --group App_Controllers

or just the Framework BaseZF:

    phpunit --configuration phpunit.xml --group BaseZF

By default, coverage reports and TestDox are generated in the ../public/debug/phpunitreport/
subdirectory.
